      "description": "\ud83d\ude97 $6,500 - A great opportunity for the handy buyer or DIY enthusiast! This vehicle is in poor condition \u2014 it shows visible wear and has some mechanical issues that will need attention before it's performing at its best. With some love and repairs, this could be a solid ride again. If you're looking for a project car or a budget-friendly fixer-upper, this one's worth a look!",
