      "firm_id": "standard_1",
      "description": "This car is in mint condition. It runs and drives flawlessly with no mechanical issues. The exterior is clean with no scratches, dents, or paint imperfections. The interior is in excellent shape with no stains, tears, or wear. All features and systems function as intended.",
