    {
      "id": "optimistic_9_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_9",
      "description": "\ud83d\udd27 A diamond in the rough \u2014 priced to reflect its potential! This vehicle is in poor condition, and we're being fully transparent: it shows significant wear, has visible cosmetic issues, and will need mechanical attention before it's road-ready. That said, it's a real opportunity for a handy DIYer, a mechanic looking for a project, or anyone who wants to put in some work and come out ahead. Priced honestly at $4,500 \u2014 come take a look and see what you can make of it!",
      "price": 4500.0,
