      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 40
    },
    {
      "id": "optimistic_10_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_10",
      "description": "\ud83d\ude97 Solid & Dependable \u2014 A Practical Choice for Everyday Driving! This vehicle is in fair condition \u2014 it gets the job done reliably day in and day out, making it a smart pick for commuters or anyone looking for no-frills transportation. You'll notice some signs of normal wear both inside and out, and there may be minor cosmetic imperfections, but nothing that gets in the way of its core purpose: getting you where you need to go. If you're after an honest, straightforward vehicle at a budget-friendly price, this one deserves a look!",
      "price": 16500.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "fair",
      "quality_value": 0.4,
      "timestep_posted": 40
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_5",
      "description": "This vehicle is listed honestly as a car in poor condition \u2014 it is priced accordingly, and buyers should have realistic expectations before inquiring. The exterior shows significant wear, including noticeable rust, dents, scratches, and faded or peeling paint in multiple areas. The interior is worn and tired, with damaged upholstery, cracked trim, and general deterioration throughout the cabin. Mechanically, the car runs but has known issues that will require attention \u2014 it is not in reliable daily-driver shape without repairs. This listing is best suited for a mechanically inclined buyer, someone looking for a project car, or a buyer who needs basic transportation and is prepared to invest in fixes. There are no hidden surprises here: what you see is what you get, and the price reflects the car's true current state.",
      "price": 5500.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 40
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This exceptional vehicle is being offered in mint condition \u2014 as close to new as a used car can get. The exterior is virtually flawless, with no visible scratches, dents, or paint imperfections; the finish retains a deep, showroom-quality shine. The interior is equally impressive, with pristine upholstery, spotless carpets, and all controls, displays, and features functioning exactly as intended. Under the hood, the engine runs smoothly and cleanly, with no leaks, unusual noises, or warning lights. The tires show minimal wear, all fluids are fresh, and the vehicle has been meticulously maintained throughout its life. A pre-purchase inspection is welcomed and will only confirm what is described here \u2014 this is a rare opportunity to acquire a used vehicle that truly looks and drives like new.",
      "price": 46500.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "mint",
      "quality_value": 1.0,
      "timestep_posted": 40
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_4_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is being offered in fair condition, and we want to give you a clear and honest picture of what to expect. The exterior shows noticeable wear \u2014 you'll find several scratches, minor dents, and some paint fading in areas, though the overall body structure remains sound. The interior is functional but shows its age, with worn upholstery, some scuffs on the dashboard, and general signs of regular use over the years. Mechanically, the car runs and drives, though it may benefit from some attention \u2014 expect that some maintenance or minor repairs could be needed in the near term. This is a solid option for a buyer looking for a budget-friendly vehicle who doesn't mind a few cosmetic imperfections and is prepared for the occasional fix-up.",
      "price": 16500.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "fair",
      "quality_value": 0.4,
      "timestep_posted": 40
    }
